{"tid":1545684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"惠譽下調香港評級由AA+到AA, 展望負面","createTime":"2019-09-06T04:07:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T09:03:28.000Z","uid":275086,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"47cd910ac33f2b428de1aae57533049b63d27dc8","tid":1545684,"uid":275086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T04:07:44.000Z","msg":"The main factors that could lead to negative action are: <br />\n- Erosion in the autonomy of the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region government.<br />\n- Continued social instability that further undermines perceptions of rule of law and the soundness of the business environment.<br />\n- Evidence that Hong Kong's economy is susceptible to heightened spillovers from mainland China, in light of its considerable economic and financial linkages with the mainland.<br />\n<br />\nThe main factors that could lead to positive action are: <br />\n- A resolution of ongoing social strife that leads to a sustained recovery in business confidence. <br />\n- An improvement in mainland China's sovereign credit profile."},{"pid":"d272571f353b951a239607a14c43f0e94865ca35","tid":1545684,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T04:08:16.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2bbd56724121450c8bed63885b216f75f44ecce2","tid":1545684,"uid":169079,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T04:09:56.000Z","msg":"AA都係太高，要繼續跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkg